### 3. 获取检测项目设置详情
GET http://localhost:8080/api/test-item-settings/1
Accept: application/json

### 4. 获取所有检测项目设置
GET http://localhost:8080/api/test-item-settings
Accept: application/json

### 5. 删除检测项目设置
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/test-item-settings/1